#!/usr/bin/env bash
set -euo pipefail

cat <<'EOF'
Counsel OS is skill-first.

There is no shell installer to run. Start Claude with this plugin loaded, then
run:

  /counsel-os:setup

The setup skill will choose or create your legal root, write the marked
{legal_root}/config.md file, seed law and practice content, and check optional
tools such as Bun and pandoc when shell access is available.
EOF
